# Datadog Progress Sender

This project is a simple Python script to send custom progress metrics to Datadog.  
It helps you visualize the progress of a job or script execution in real time on Datadog dashboards.

## ðŸš€ Features

- Send custom progress metrics (e.g., 10%, 20%, ..., 100%) to Datadog
- Use environment variables to securely manage Datadog API keys
- Easy integration with Datadog dashboards

## ðŸ“¦ Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- Datadog account and API Key

